      <title>三星电子与德州仪器确定芯片法案奖项</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/texas-instruments-finalizes-chips-act-award-gets-1-6-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[三星电子公司和德州仪器公司达成最终协议，将获得政府数十亿美元的支持，用于在美国建立新的半导体工厂，巩固了拜登政府“芯片法案”倡议的重要部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/texas-instruments-finalizes-chips-act-award-gets-1-6-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 18:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
