      <title>AT&T 希望向固话用户推销一款新型家用电话</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/at-t-hopes-to-sell-copper-holdouts-on-a-new-kind-of-home-phone</link>
      <description><![CDATA[AT&amp;T 公司希望在 2029 年底之前说服全国人民摆脱固定电话的困扰。为了实现这一目标，该公司正在部署一种可能有帮助的新武器：无线家用电话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/at-t-hopes-to-sell-copper-holdouts-on-a-new-kind-of-home-phone</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 14:26:55 GMT</pubDate>
